{
  "id": "adv_card_mhk_01_03",
  "title": "miho 3話 一泡吹かせてやる",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――アイドルイベント打ち合わせの日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Day of Idol Event meeting",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 5.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "本日は、お時間いただきありがとうございます\n……ⅢXのmihoです、よろしくお願いいたします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for your time today.\n…I'm miho from IIIX. Nice to meet you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "プロデューサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Producer",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03-producer001.m4a",
      "text": "こちらこそ、お二人にお会い出来て光栄ですよ\nそれでは、来月のイベントの詳細なのですが――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The pleasure is mine. It's an honor to meet both of you.\nNow‚ let's go into the details of next month's event…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "プロデューサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Producer",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03-producer002.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、それでは星見プロさんからは\nTRINITYAiLEとⅢXということで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ from Hoshimi Pro…\nWith TRINITYAiLE and IIIX…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "…………当日は、精一杯やらせていただきます\nよろしくお願いしますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I will do my best on the day of the event.\nPlease support us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "プロデューサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Producer",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03-producer003.m4a",
      "text": "サニーピースは残念でしたが、BIG4に次ぐ勢いの\nトリエルが出てくれるなら間違いなく盛り上がりますな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Unfortunately the Sunny Peace is not able to come‚\nbut if we have a strong group like TRINITYAiLE‚ it will definitely be exciting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます。でも、星見プロには\n個性的なグループがまだまだいるんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you. However‚ Hoshimi Pro still has unique groups.\nDon't miss the chance to promote them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "……売り込む機会を逃さないのね\n熱心なマネージャーさんだこと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're such an enthusiastic manager.\nNot letting any opportunities slip by.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "例えば、月のテンペストの長瀬琴乃は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For example‚ Kotono Nagase from Moon Tempest…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "プロデューサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Producer",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03-producer004.m4a",
      "text": "はは……さすが、有力なグループをいくつも抱えていて\n羨ましいことですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha… As expected‚\nit's enviable to have multiple powerful groups.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "……随分と喋ったわね\nプロデューサー、呆れてるじゃない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "….You've talked quite a bit.\nThe producer looks exasperated…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そしてⅢXは、『女性が憧れる女性』がコンセプトです\nうちのグループの中でも女性ファンが凄く多いですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And for IIIX‚ the concept is \"the women that women admire.\"\nAmong our group‚ they have a lot of female fans.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "歌もダンスも完璧に計算され尽くしている、その\nステージを作り上げているのが、mihoさんなんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "miho-san is the one creating a stage that is perfectly calculated and\npolished in terms of singing and dancing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "え…………\nあ、ありがとうございます……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh…\nTh-Thank you…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "プロデューサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Producer",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03-producer005.m4a",
      "text": "しかし、ⅢXはI-UNITYの一件もありますから\n集客力も落ちてますし、もう……『過去の人』でしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However‚ IIIX has also been affected by the I-UNITY incident.\nTheir drawing power has declined‚ and they are now… \"people of the past.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "……力不足で、申し訳ありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I apologize for the lack of strength.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "――お言葉ですが\nⅢXは過去ではなく、これからのグループです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With all due respect…\nIIIX is not a group of the past but a group of the future.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…{user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "前にいた事務所で、いろいろあったのは確かですが\n必ず挽回して、以前より上に行けると俺は信じています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's true that there were various things that happened in the previous agency‚\nbut I believe we can make a comeback and go higher than before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.6333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6266.6666667000045,
          "startTime": 124.9
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6266.6666667000045,
          "startTime": 124.9
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 124.7
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 124.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "……まさか、貴方が私達のことまで\n売り込んでくれるとは思いませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I never expected\nyou to promote us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 132.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "……貴方は、私達を嫌っていると思っていましたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I thought you disliked us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃ今でも、あの一件に思うところはありますよ\nでも、それとアイドルとしての評価は別物です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ there are still some lingering thoughts about that incident.\nBut that's separate from evaluating you as idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 144.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "……そう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I see.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 146.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、自分が担当しているアイドルとはいえ\nよく全員分、すらすらと出てくるものですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it's impressive that you can effortlessly\npromote all the idols you are in charge of.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 153.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
