      "text": "俺は星見プロみんなの一番のファンでいたいし\nマネージャーはそうあるべきだと思っています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to be the number one fan of all the members at Hoshimi Pro.\nAnd I think that's what a manager should be.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.4666666667,
