      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "それはご立派ですけど\n星見プロにいる子は、決して少なくはないのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's commendable‚\nbut there are many idols at Hoshimi Pro.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
