      "text": "また転ぶんですね！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're falling again‚ aren't you?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 296.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 300.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03-mhk030.m4a",
      "text": "改めて、ⅢXです\n今日は、私達の歌を聴いてくれてありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello‚ we are IIIX.\nThank you for listening to our songs today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 304.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03-mhk031.m4a",
      "text": "全力で歌って、沢山の人に応援してもらって\n今の私達に出来る、最高のステージを作れたと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We sang with all our might‚ and thanks to the support from everyone‚\nI believe we created the best stage we could.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 312.0666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3566.6666666000424,
