        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "（……凄い熱気だな）\n（落ち目なんてとんでもない、これがスリクスの実力だ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…The energy is incredible.）\n（ It's wrong to say that they have fallen. This is the true talent of IIIX.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 319.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03-mhk032.m4a",
      "text": "でも、これで満足するつもりはありません\n次のステージではもっと進化して、その次だって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However‚ I'm not satisfied with just this.\nIn the next stage‚ we will evolve further‚ and even after that‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 328.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_03-mhk033.m4a",
      "text": "その途中で、また何度も失敗するのでしょうけど\nでもそれも糧にして、いつか――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There may be times when we fail along the way‚\nBut we will use those as stepping stones‚ and eventually…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 337.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
